-I hope it's not a girl.

109
00:07:13.916 --> 00:07:14.750
I mean it.

110
00:07:15.666 --> 00:07:18.125
It's not a girl. It's a warrior.

111
00:07:19.125 --> 00:07:20.416
She kicks. just like you do.

112
00:07:20.500 --> 00:07:21.583
