256
00:22:21.208 --> 00:22:22.041
Pick up.

257
00:23:52.666 --> 00:23:54.125
This way. run!

258
00:24:05.500 --> 00:24:07.083
Watch out! It's coming loose.

259
00:24:07.166 --> 00:24:08.000
Help!

260
00:24:08.083 --> 00:24:10.250
Help!

261
00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:12.875
